findings.title: Block gas limit
findings.description: add(uint256 _allocPoint, …) and set(uint256 _pid, …) could invoke massUpdatePools() function, which can fail due to block gas limit if the pool size is too big.

findings.title: Owner privileges (In the period when the owner is not renounced)
findings.description: The contract owner and operator have excessive privileges to modify critical parameters, including kennyEthPair, transfer tax rate, minimum liquidity amount, autoLiquidity, devAddress, and feeAddress.
